# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the united states welcomed on tuesday an agreement reached during the weekend by ukraine 's rival leaders to hold elections on sept. ## .
# ::alignments
(w / welcome-01
      :ARG0 (c / country
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "United"
                  :op2 "States"))
      :ARG1 (a / agree-01
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :ARG0-of (l / lead-02
                        :ARG1 (c2 / country
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Ukraine")))
                  :ARG0-of (r / rival-01
                        :ARG1 c2))
            :ARG1 (h / hold-04
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (e / elect-01
                        :time (d / date-entity
                              :dayperiod (n3 / night))))
            :ARG1-of (r2 / reach-01
                  :time (w2 / weekend)))
      :time d
      :weekday (t / tuesday))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok attorneys for sniper mastermind john allen muhammad are asking the u.s. supreme court to stop his execution scheduled for next week .
# ::alignments
(a / ask-02
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-rel-role-91
                  :ARG1 (p2 / person
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "John"
                              :op2 "Allen"
                              :op3 "Muhammad")
                        :ARG0-of (m / mastermind-01
                              :ARG1 (s / sniper)))
                  :ARG2 (a2 / attorney)))
      :ARG1 (s2 / stop-01
            :ARG0 (g / government-organization
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "U.S."
                        :op2 "Supreme"
                        :op3 "Court"))
            :ARG1 (e / execute-01
                  :ARG1 p2
                  :ARG1-of (s3 / schedule-01
                        :ARG3 (w / week
                              :mod (n3 / next)))))
      :ARG2 g)

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok adding to fears that a mystery flu-like illness is being spread by air travelers , hong kong officials said tuesday nine tourists apparently came down with the deadly disease after a mainland chinese man infected them on a flight to beijing .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (c / company
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Hong"
                              :op2 "Kong"))
                  :ARG2 (o / official)))
      :ARG1 (a / appear-02
            :ARG1 (c2 / come-down-23
                  :ARG1 (p2 / person
                        :quant 9
                        :ARG0-of (t / tour-01))
                  :ARG2 (d / disease
                        :ARG0-of (k / kill-01))
                  :time (a2 / after
                        :op1 (ii / infect-01
                              :ARG0 (m / man
                                    :mod (m2 / mainland)
                                    :mod (c3 / country
                                          :name (n2 / name
                                                :op1 "China")))
                              :ARG1 p2
                              :time (f / fly-01
                                    :destination (c4 / city
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "Beijing")))))))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (t2 / tuesday))
      :ARG0-of (a3 / add-02
            :ARG2 (f2 / fear-01
                  :ARG1 (s2 / spread-03
                        :ARG0 (p3 / person
                              :ARG0-of (t3 / travel-01
                                    :ARG4 (a4 / air)))
                        :ARG1 (ii2 / ill-01
                              :ARG1-of (r / resemble-01
                                    :ARG2 d
                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 "influenza")))
                        :mod (m3 / mystery)))))

                  :ARG2 (o / official)))
      :ARG1 (l / let-01
            :ARG0 b
            :ARG1 (m / move-01
                  :ARG1 (r / rate
                        :mod (o2 / official)
                        :mod (e / exchange-01
                              :ARG1 (c3 / currency
                                    :poss c2)))
                  :ARG2 (c4 / close-10
                        :ARG1 r
                        :ARG2 r
                        :mod (e2 / exchange-01
                              :ARG1 (m2 / market)))
                  :ARG2-of (h2 / have-degree-91
                        :ARG1 r
                        :ARG3 (m3 / more)))
            :ARG0-of (f / fulfill-01
                  :ARG1 (t / thing
                        :ARG1-of (c5 / condition-01
                              :ARG2 (r2 / receive-01
                                    :ARG1 (m4 / monetary-quantity
                                          :ARG1-of (f2 / fund-01)
                                          :mod (ii / international)))
                              :ARG1-of (k / key-02)))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (f3 / friday)))

# ::id 4 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Russia"))

                  :ARG1 (a / and
                        :op1 (s / satellite
                              :mod c)
                        :op2 (f / foreign)
                        :purpose (o / orbit-01
                              :ARG1 (a2 / and
                                    :op1 (c3 / country
                                          :name (n2 / name
                                                :op1 "Iran"))
                                    :op2 (c4 / country
                                          :name (n3 / name
                                                :op1 "China"))
                                    :op3 (o2 / other))))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (t / thursday))
      :direction (o3 / off))

                                                :name (n3 / name
                                                      :op1 "Medicare")))
                                    :ARG1-of (h4 / have-degree-91
                                          :ARG2 (w / wealthy)
                                          :ARG3 (m2 / more))))))
            :manner (a / and

                        :ARG0 p

                  :op2 (p8 / pledge-01

# ::id 9 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                        :poss (c / country
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "America"))

                              :name (n2 / name

                                    :op2 "brains")))

                        :ARG1-of (g / gay-01)
                        :mod (l / lesbian))
                  :time (g2 / game
                        :time (d / date-entity
                              :weekday (w / wednesday))
                        :poss t
                        :mod t
                        :name (n3 / name
                              :op1 "Houston"
                              :op2 "Astros")))))

                        :quant 9

                  :ARG1 (l / leak-01

                              :mod (h / hydraulic)))
                  :time (a / after
                        :op1 (l2 / launch-01
                              :ARG1 s2))))
      :time (d4 / date-entity
            :weekday (f2 / friday)))

      :ARG1 (p / person

                  :op2 "Richardson")

                  :ARG2 (s / secretary
                        :topic (e / energy))))
      :ARG4 (h2 / here)
      :purpose (v / visit-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1-of (s2 / short-07)
            :part-of (t / tour-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (c / country
                        :location (w / world-region
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Gulf"))
                        :ARG0-of (h3 / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 (o / organization
                                    :mod (c2 / country
                                          :ARG0-of (e2 / export-01
                                                :ARG1 (p2 / petroleum))))
                              :ARG2 (m / member)))))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (s3 / sunday)))
